haReport:
This mission was flown by:
Kmdr Patrik Schorner
Ltn Augustus Kass
Ltn Johann Hanneman
Fw Ruprecht Hess

 The mission was flown from Balatre aerodrome.

Successes include the following: 
On 30/07/1916 near Ypres.
A F.E.2b of No 16 Squadron RFC was brought down by Florian Lasch of Jasta 16b.
2nd Lt Sebastian Nysell was killed in action.
Lt Brock Bladewell was killed in action.
Florian Lasch was  flying a Halberstadt D.II.
